(LOL) I was in High Keep a couple of weeks ago, looking for a group as usual.  I had my lfg tag on, and wandered down to the basement.  There were four others sitting there with their tag on, just looking around.  I looked at them...they looked at me.  I finally asked what class/level they all were.  Turns out we were all within 3 seasons, so I invited them all to group.<br>
<br>
I was amazed that they were all just sitting around looking for a group, but didn't try to group with each other, when the main room in the basement was uncamped.  I could understand if every room was camped and they were waiting for group spots to open up, but to just sit there while spawns were going to waste?  Go figure.<br>
<br>
